name: الصين تُرعب أمريكا: روبوتات بشرية، مدن ذكية، سيارات خارقة، وذكاء اصطناعي! 🇨🇳
description:
🇨🇳 نظرة داخل ثورة التكنولوجيا في الصين: ٤ مدن مستقبلية تقود العالم

🔹 شينجن – "وادي السيليكون الآسيوي"
سيارات ذاتية القيادة، توصيل بالطائرات بدون طيار، الدفع بكف اليد — وزيارة حصرية إلى شركة BYD، عملاق السيارات الكهربائية الذي تفوّق على تيسلا.
🔹 هانغتشو – حيث تلتقي الطبيعة بالتكنولوجيا
من بحيرة ويست ليك الخلابة إلى روبوت G1 من Unitree: روبوت بشري يجري بسرعة ٥ أمتار في الثانية، ويتمتع برؤية ٣٦٠ درجة.
🔹 شنغهاي – المحرك الاقتصادي للصين
مركز مالي عالمي يقوده الذكاء الاصطناعي والبنية التحتية للمدن الذكية.
🔹 جينان (شاندونغ) – صعود الذكاء الاصطناعي الشبيه بالبشر
داخل مختبرات تطوّر روبوتات بملامح بشرية، تعبيرات وجه، ومشاعر وتفاعل واقعي.

لم يعد الشعار "صُنع في الصين"...
بل أصبح: "اختُرع في الصين".

name: Highlights | Guyana Amazon Warriors vs Rangpur Riders | GSL 2025
description:
Highlights between the Guyana Amazon Warriors and the Rangpur Riders in the GSL 2025 at Providence Stadium in Guyana. 

The Global Super League (GSL) T20 2025 returns for its second year in Guyana, featuring five teams from around the globe. This year's teams are Caribbean Premier League side Guyana Amazon Warriors, Dubai Capitals winners of the International League T20, GSL defending champions Rangpur Riders from the Bangladesh Premier League, Central Districts from the Super Smash in New Zealand, and Big Bash League Champions Hobart Hurricanes XI from Australia. Eleven matches, including the final, will be played across as many days starting July 10, with each team playing the other once before the top two make the final on July 19. Don’t miss any of the action of this unique cricket competition, where the Caribbean atmosphere meets some of the best T20 cricketers to create a sporting spectacle. Look out for live matches, highlights, extended highlights, best moments, compilations, interviews and more!

ABOUT CHELSEA FOOTBALL CLUB 

Founded in 1905, Chelsea Football Club is an English professional football club based in Fulham, West London with Stamford Bridge as the home of the club. Competing in the Premier League - the top division of English football, the club has had many successes, winning five Premier League titles. The club won their first major honour, the League championship in 1955, followed by the FA Cup in 1970, their first European honour, the Cup Winners' Cup in 1971, and became the third English club to win the Club World Cup in 2022. 

As the Pride of London, Chelsea FC is one of the most successful clubs in terms of overall trophies won. They are the only club to have won all three major European competitions twice and have taken the crown domestically, winning six league titles, eight FA Cups, five League Cups, and four FA Community Shields. Internationally, Chelsea have won the UEFA Champions League, the UEFA Europa League, the UEFA Cup Winners' Cup and the UEFA Super Cup twice each, and the FIFA Club World Cup once since their inception.

The Chelsea YouTube channel provides access to all the build-up, training and behind-the-scenes moments and matchday action along with all the unseen edits and player focus from Reece James, Cole Palmer and Enzo Fernandez to Sam Kerr, Lauren James and many more. It’s the only channel where you’ll get an authentic look at this great club including memorable nights with world-class heroes such as Peter Osgood, Gianfranco Zola, Frank Lampard, John Terry, Didier Drogba & Eden Hazard.
